dashboard.description: Stats from FlexSwitch side of the house

targets.query: SELECT non_negative_derivative(mean("usage_iowait"), 1s) FROM "cpu" WHERE "host" =~ /^$server$/ AND "cpu" = 'cpu-total' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval) fill(null)
SELECT first("ProductName") FROM "platform" WHERE "host" =~ /^$server$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT count("NumPortsUp") FROM "asicsum" WHERE "host" =~ /^$server$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT count("NumPortsDown") FROM "asicsum" WHERE "host" =~ /^$server$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT count("NumPortsDown") FROM "asicsum" WHERE "host" =~ /^$server$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT difference("IfEtherBcastPkts") FROM "ports" WHERE "host" =~ /^$server$/ AND "port" =~ /^$fpPort$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT difference("IfEtherBcastPkts") FROM "ports" WHERE "host" =~ /^$server$/ AND "port" =~ /^$fpPort$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

list.label: Server

list.label: Front Panel interface

list.label: FlexSwitch Daemon

list.label: FlexSwitch Management IP

list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "platform" WITH KEY = "mgmt-ip" WHERE host =~ /$server/

list.label: Vlan ID
